title: Side Effects of Fatherhood (with Dwayne “DW” Wright)
description:
This week we’re joined by bass player, Music Director for, “Smart Funny & Black”, and father of two boys, Dwayne “DW” Wright to get a millennial parenting POV on how to be the world’s greatest Dad.
